{"type":null,"faqId":37117,"title":"如何避免手环屏幕划伤、刮花、磕碰？手环B2_屏幕有裂缝怎么办？底托后盖翘起故障如何处理？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、,B2产品是经过严格的抗划伤和耐磨测试的，而且B2出厂前，屏幕都是默认增加保护膜的，使用时请避免将手环与钥匙等易划伤屏幕的金属物品放在一起（请像爱护手机屏幕一样爱护你的手环的屏幕噢）。建议佩戴时注意磕碰，放置时小心手环跌落。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、屏幕有裂缝：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（1）确定是否人为撞损？</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（2）按照流程上升CSE</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、屏幕显示有竖线及底托后盖翘起怎么办？</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>底托后盖翘起：请拍图回传至热线客服邮箱，确保图片能表现所描述的问题。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>研发EHP期间，如图片描述属实，请上升至CSE。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">B2手环屏幕无法完全显示？B2屏幕亮度是否能调节？B2的屏幕可不可以换成彩色的？</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、B2手环屏幕无法完全显示或显示不全：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（1）尝试开机重启，通过手机将手机APP和手环更新至最新版本。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（2）按照流程上升CSE</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、屏幕暂不支持亮度调节，请期待后续版本</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、屏幕暂时不支持彩色，我们会参考您的建议在下一代的产品考虑。非常感谢您的支持和反馈。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2281","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750143000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":561,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,屏幕显示一半,显示不全","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}